.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-CAPACITY-SUM" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-capacity-sum \- FEAT-2858 sum of channel capacity per peer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-capacity-sum
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the sum of total_msat across all channels grouped by peer (FEAT-2858).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
